sentences: He was born in Asunción, capital of Paraguay, on March 9, 1929 to Ramón Zayas and Ramona Román.
Zayas died in Asunción, Paraguay on September 19, 2001.
For many years he wrote a column about traditions and folklore of Paraguay called "Parrilla Luna y Folklore".
He was a columnist for the newspaper Ultima Hora and has published more than 150 articles that are compiled in the book “Parrilla, Luna y Folklore” (Asunción 1995).
